Puppet Java Module
===================

Introduction
-----------

Pupept module to install java

## Usage ##

Install sun java or openjdk packages

class { java:
 java_package_type = 'sun',
 java_version = '6',
}

Notes
-----

This module is written only for redhat based systems.
Module is written primarily for CentOS/Redhat-6, java-6 installation is only supported for CentOS/Redhat-5 version.

Requirements: 
------------

* puppet-stdlib module is required to get this module working
* example42-yum module is required to get this module working


